        // If n is even, this partition is not valid.
        // However, the problem asks for *any* partition.
        //
        // The crucial observation is that the median of a class of size $2k+1$ is the $(k+1)$-th element.
        // If we sort the entire array $a_0, \dots, a_{2n-1}$, the elements $a_{n-1}$ and $a_n$ are the two
